        Know what your <b> rent control </b> is worth 
    </h1>
    <p class="font-medium text-white">
      Determine the value of your rent control in minutes. Simply enter your name and apartment details, and weâ€™ll pull the latest market information about relocation payments in your neighborhood. Easier than getting Kelly Blue Book estimate.
